Input Format

The first line of input will contain an integer TTT — the number of test cases. The description of TTT test cases follows.
The first and only line of each test case contains two space-separated integers XXX and YYY, as described in the problem statement.


Output Format
For each test case, output on a new line the total amount of money that Chef will have to pay.

Constraints


